;Motivation

Eldoblaje is a well-known database of films dubbed in Spanish. There's already a property in Wikidata about films, so with new properties actors and voice actors can be added too. [[User:Escudero|Escudero]] ([[User talk:Escudero|<span class="signature-talk">{{int:Talkpagelinktext}}</span>]]) 23:15, 13 October 2017 (UTC)
